<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>سُورَةُ الْمَاعُونِ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>بِسْمِ اللَّهِ الرَّحْمَنِ الرَّحِيمِ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">قَالَ تَعَالَى:</span> <span class="c2">(فَذَلِكَ الَّذِي يَدُعُّ الْيَتِيمَ (٢)</span>) .<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">قَوْلُهُ تَعَالَى:</span> <span class="c2">(فَذَلِكَ)</span> : الْفَاءُ جَوَابُ شَرْطٍ مُقَدَّرٌ،<span class="c5"> تَقْدِيرُهُ:</span> إِنْ تَأَمَّلْتَهُ، أَوْ إِنْ طَلَبْتَ عِلْمَهُ. وَ <span class="c2">(يَدُعُّ)</span> -<span class="c5"> بِالتَّشْدِيدِ:</span> يَدْفَعُ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>وَقُرِئَ بِفَتْحِ الدَّالِ وَتَخْفِيفِ الْعَيْنِ؛ أَيْ يُهْمِلُهُ. وَاللَّهُ أَعْلَمُ<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>